{"id":543946,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Giorgio_Albertazzi","text":"Giorgio Albertazzi (20 August 1923 \u2013 28 May 2016) was an Italian actor movie director, screenwriter and singer.\nHe was known for his roles in \"Little World of Don Camillo\", \"Concert of Intrigue\", \"White Nights\", \"Last Year at Marienbad\", \"Eva\", \"Redhead\", \"I Married You for Fun\", \"The Assassination of Trotsky\", \"Five Women for the Killer\", \"Mark of the Cop\", \"Once a Year, Every Year\", \"Li chiamarono... briganti!\", \"The Rage\" and in \"Some Say No\".\nHis best known directed movies were \"La governante\" and \"Gradiva\". He sang the soundtrack for \"Gli angeli del potere\".\nAlbertazzi died on 28 May 2016 in Roccastrada, Italy, aged 92.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Italians","surface_form":"Italian","offset":57},{"uri":"Little_World_of_Don_Camillo","surface_form":"Little World of Don Camillo","offset":143},{"uri":"Concert_of_Intrigue","surface_form":"Concert of Intrigue","offset":174},{"uri":"White_Nights_(1957_movie)","surface_form":"White Nights","offset":197},{"uri":"Last_Year_at_Marienbad","surface_form":"Last Year at Marienbad","offset":213},{"uri":"Eva_(1962_movie)","surface_form":"Eva","offset":239},{"uri":"Redhead_(movie)","surface_form":"Redhead","offset":246},{"uri":"I_Married_You_for_Fun","surface_form":"I Married You for Fun","offset":257},{"uri":"The_Assassination_of_Trotsky","surface_form":"The Assassination of Trotsky","offset":282},{"uri":"Five_Women_for_the_Killer","surface_form":"Five Women for the Killer","offset":314},{"uri":"Mark_of_the_Cop","surface_form":"Mark of the Cop","offset":343},{"uri":"Once_a_Year%2C_Every_Year","surface_form":"Once a Year, Every Year","offset":362},{"uri":"Li_chiamarono..._briganti%21","surface_form":"Li chiamarono... briganti!","offset":389},{"uri":"The_Rage_(2008_movie)","surface_form":"The Rage","offset":419},{"uri":"Some_Say_No","surface_form":"Some Say No","offset":437},{"uri":"